library(ggmap)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
library(mapproj)
## Loading required package: maps
library(dplyr)

source('TWD97TM2toWGS84.R')

map <- get_map(location=c(lon=121.543331, lat=25.028017), zoom=14, language = "zh-TW")
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=25.028017,121.543331&zoom=14&size=640x640&scale=2&maptype=terrain&language=zh-TW&sensor=false

data <- read.csv(file="free_net.csv")

ggmap(map, darken = c(0.6, "white")) + 
  geom_point(aes(x=, y=, color=, size=.M.), data=data%>% filter( == ""))+
  ggtitle("")+
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size =20))
